Barbara Nichols https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Nichols 0 Barbara Marie Nickerauer (December 10, 1928 – October 5, 1976), better known as Barbara Nichols, was an American actress who often played brassy or comic roles in films in the 1950s and 1960s.
